Sentencas: In this work, abundant oxygen vacancies are introduced into NdBaCo2O5+delta (NBCO) by partial substitution of cobalt to facilitate the electrochemical activity of ORR.
Titulo: Probing oxygen vacancy effect on oxygen reduction reaction of the NdBaCo2O5+δ cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The oxygen vacancy concentration of NdBaCo1.8Sc0.2O5+delta (NBCSc-2) is more than twice as that of NdBaCo2O5+delta.
Titulo: Probing oxygen vacancy effect on oxygen reduction reaction of the NdBaCo2O5+δ cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The increased oxygen surface exchange, bulk diffusion coefficients and adequate conductivity for NBCSc-2 can be responsible for the decrease of oxygen ion transfer activation energy.
Titulo: Probing oxygen vacancy effect on oxygen reduction reaction of the NdBaCo2O5+δ cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Consequently, the NBCSc-2 cathode shows a significantly reduced polarization impedance of 0.035 Omega cm(2) at 700 degrees C, which is only about 35% of NBCO.
Titulo: Probing oxygen vacancy effect on oxygen reduction reaction of the NdBaCo2O5+δ cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: We also investigate the influence of the doping strategy on the stability of cathode.
Titulo: Probing oxygen vacancy effect on oxygen reduction reaction of the NdBaCo2O5+δ cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Thus, the enhanced ORR kinetics and high durability make NBCSc-2 as potential cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Probing oxygen vacancy effect on oxygen reduction reaction of the NdBaCo2O5+δ cathode for solid oxide fuel cells
